Non Policy Document
Code used to enable the transmission of eDocs that are unrelated to a specific policy or individual.  Some of the documents that carriers might send using this method include (but are not restricted to): 
• monthly summaries of policies, claims or commissions; 
• promotions for new markets or lines of business; 
• notifications of underwriting changes; 
• reconciliation statements; 
• messages intended for a specific group of policies, accounts or employees

